	<h1 class="title">下次去东京，到这个大书柜里住一晚？</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/101857/small/101857.jpg?1429073860" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">谢舒敏 </span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-10-27 12:21:42 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/16646/medium/16646.jpg?1445918979" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


<div class="com-share" data-id="16646" data-title="《下次去东京，到这个大书柜里住一晚？》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/16646/medium/16646.jpg?1445918979" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/16646.html" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
